Subject: [PATCH] HID: logitech-dj: add the G602 receiver
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e400071a805d6229223a98899e9da8c6233704a1
Patch-mainline: v5.11-rc4
References: git-fixes

Tested. The device gets correctly exported to userspace and I can see
mouse and keyboard events.

Signed-off-by: Filipe La√≠ns <lains@archlinux.org>
Signed-off-by: Jiri Kosina <jkosina@suse.cz>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 drivers/hid/hid-logitech-dj.c |    4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

--- a/drivers/hid/hid-logitech-dj.c
+++ b/drivers/hid/hid-logitech-dj.c
@@ -1871,6 +1871,10 @@ static const struct hid_device_id logi_d
 	  HID_USB_DEVICE(USB_VENDOR_ID_LOGITECH,
 		USB_DEVICE_ID_LOGITECH_27MHZ_MOUSE_RECEIVER),
 	 .driver_data = recvr_type_27mhz},
+	{ /* Logitech G602 receiver (0xc537) */
+	  HID_USB_DEVICE(USB_VENDOR_ID_LOGITECH,
+		0xc537),
+	 .driver_data = recvr_type_gaming_hidpp},
 	{ /* Logitech MX5000 HID++ / bluetooth receiver keyboard intf. */
 	  HID_USB_DEVICE(USB_VENDOR_ID_LOGITECH,
 		0xc70e),
